{"tid":809661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港媽鬧員工在餐廳霸位用膳 網友：人哋都係打份工","createTime":"2018-09-07T10:46:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T16:38:59.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"359295d58b4827e72706a37555636d3f289c19ba","tid":809661,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T10:46:28.000Z","msg":"昨日，有港媽於「屯門友Facebook專頁」發文投訴餐廳員工霸佔坐位用餐，當時，正值中午12時，餐廳都滿坐，在她「推住bb車帶兩個小朋友」等位等足5分鐘的情況下，正在用膳的兩名員工仍無動於衷，「霸佐（口一3張4人檯」、「霸住位睇手機」。<br />\n<br />\n網友回應：人哋都係打份工<br />\n<br />\n發文引來不少網民回應，有人同情員工「人哋都係打份工」，表示員工吃飯用座位合理，員工和客人應一視同仁，無分等級。更有網民指，該名港媽可以禮貌上前詢問可否「搭枱」，而不是「影人相」。有網民指餐廳員工工作辛苦，在午飯時間休息都要「俾人當批鬥座公審」，實在不太公平。<br />\n<br />\n雖然港媽當時要同時要照顧兩個小朋友，亦不容易，但須體諒員工工作的辛苦，上前溝通清楚，相信員工亦會儘快讓出位置。"},{"pid":"a1cd80a1fcdbd93e2ead94ab3595591385d299f8","tid":809661,"uid":19552,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T10:47:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tdR8jqChzv4Ebw8__kezZg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQ4MS4zMDA4MTMwMDgxMzAx/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/qIH7r5k0.Qoa1dwLsrKa.g--~B/aD0zNzA7dz00OTI7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/sunday_kiss_359/0a65ce4f0a65ed2f8ac4ce052553fc8e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FtdR8jqChzv4Ebw8__kezZg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQ4MS4zMDA4MTMwMDgxMzAx%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FqIH7r5k0.Qoa1dwLsrKa.g--~B%2FaD0zNzA7dz00OTI7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fsunday_kiss_359%2F0a65ce4f0a65ed2f8ac4ce052553fc8e&h=745761c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55148ec7172ff5c24bec54f9681dd62649dcb7c8","tid":809661,"uid":41368,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T10:48:01.000Z","msg":"香港人種真係好自我中心"},{"pid":"8562338f02836ac96b69ee39a14316296880fd3d","tid":809661,"uid":810,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T10:49